{"tid":401383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（痴撚線）香港美心月餅唔可以睇澳門賣","createTime":"2017-09-15T14:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T20:54:11.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86cebb1cd3714d4e8f9961d4ebde8666e57c7f3b","tid":401383,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"澳門海關早前接獲權利人舉報，指有人以代購形式，出售涉嫌侵犯其商標的月餅產品。由於該品牌商標已在澳門經濟局合法註冊登記，海關收到舉報後，立即展開調查，並於前日(13日)採取行動，分別在兩間店舖內，查獲一批涉嫌侵犯「美心月餅」商標權的月餅，合共314盒，市值約8萬多澳門元。<br />\n關員帶走涉案兩名人士到海關總部協助調查，兩人均為澳門居民，女性，其中一人姓李(42歲)，另一人姓吳(30歲)。兩人涉嫌觸犯第97/99/M號法令《工業產權法律制度》第292條（將產品或物品出售、流通或隱藏）所指之犯罪，海關將對相關人士作出起訴，並移送司法機關處理。<br />\n案中涉嫌侵犯「美心月餅」商標權的「香港美心月餅」，在香港已註冊登記，可在港銷售，惟在澳銷售則因侵犯權利人在澳門已註冊的商標權，故屬違法。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170915&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57215777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170915%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57215777&d=VDZ0rhTfcdrDQN359Iz3HZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dae2efa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170915%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57215777&h=0bd79234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170915&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57215777</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/222537_2b86e353c1fd0a7a7bb27a923f91c147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F222537_2b86e353c1fd0a7a7bb27a923f91c147.jpg&h=d0b74dc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d088a2cd97859a45b80bc952113b11c3f049533e","tid":401383,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"澳門狗"},{"pid":"65790dcc95f82f9d62aa0f7a5cab4b1db4831744","tid":401383,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"同大陸一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e13fbe3b746f35abe7b1044be20b2a7b04aac6","tid":401383,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"澳門嘅「美心月餅」，係由「澳門美心餅店有限公司」製造及銷售。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef0da1fd51f51b6b343241585c7f628e4b0136a","tid":401383,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"睇住澳門賣有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df857800699cd6b6520ffab2b0e16b9eaf1b7493","tid":401383,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇住澳門賣有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳門人只能到本港，買「香港美心月餅」返澳門自用；<br />\n但於澳門當地發售「香港美心月餅」牟利，就會觸犯「澳門美心餅店」嘅商標權。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9891271006c922b15d501a8ee611e973c9ab6fbf","tid":401383,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"好明顯澳門美心同香港美心係無關係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005131b907d77112684a5a515f12dddf8ed71b72","tid":401383,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好明顯澳門美心同香港美心係無關係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就好似「黃金月餅」同「金黃月餅」嘅分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fc75b67f84ac231f13b072d756e889a89327c6","tid":401383,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"支澳"},{"pid":"deae3cda437c320ef4804e39678462d91563b741","tid":401383,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:21:49.000Z","msg":"喬丹<br />\n<br />\n新栢倫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39becfc4bbbacf68e40a601b85c2d9ce2335d79a","tid":401383,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:28:06.000Z","msg":"都係大陸人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be939660644bbfe726ac1d57d20050c480b941e","tid":401383,"uid":2394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:34:32.000Z","msg":"抵撚死。水貨狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6fc4cda60927c65eac81336a47d9dab58d7d56","tid":401383,"uid":9321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇住澳門賣有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳門人只能到本港，買「香港美心月餅」返澳門自用；<br />\n但於澳門當地發售「香港美心月餅」牟利，就會觸犯「澳門美心餅店」嘅商標權。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當水貨賣唔得？最多咪無保養 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b78b439cf1403aec8d1ca735df62aa83376ef9","tid":401383,"uid":39347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇住澳門賣有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳門人只能到本港，買「香港美心月餅」返澳門自用；<br />\n但於澳門當地發售「香港美心月餅」牟利，就會觸犯「澳門美心餅店」嘅商標權。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下 即係同一個商標分左兩間店係兩個地方用<br />\n如果賣水貨就即係自己打自己?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb093c72a892ffbcc1b46bdf26df259f4e4f555","tid":401383,"uid":52675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"周六福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094a52be59bd67dd44b59333310b4d616669763f","tid":401383,"uid":83709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:46:35.000Z","